name: Algonquin
tagline: Repo for Algonquin's course on Git.
body:
#Algonquin
####Public pages for school projects

##This Repo
This repo is the combination of course work put together for Algonquin's *MTM4086 - Rich Internet Services*. Covered in the course are Git, page speed optimizations, AJAX, and CSS preprocessors. Each folder contains a submission for an assignment.

##The Prof
This course was expertly taught by @brandonbrule.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
